== Description == <!--T:11-->

<!--T:2-->
The [[Image:Draft_Snap_Angle.svg|24px]] '''Draft Snap Angle''' option snaps to the special cardinal points on circular edges, at multiples of 30° and 45°. The edges can belong to [[Draft_Workbench|Draft]] or [[BIM_Workbench|BIM]] objects but also to objects created with other [[Workbenches|workbenches]].

